title: PZBGIS.CITY_BNDRY
name: PZBGIS.CITY_BNDRY
description: This data set contains the boundaries of all 38 municipalities in Palm Beach County.  Boundaries are accurate according to feedback from each municipality.  Accuracy is to street centerlines, canal centerlines and parcel lines.  The boundaries are not accurate with regards to rights-of-way.  The majority of the City polygons go to the right-of-way centerline, but this is only for aesthetic purposes and to present a seamless polygon layer.
